graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Operator<br/>Job Queue Manager]

    %% Required External Dependencies
    Kueue -->|REQUIRED<br/>watches CRDs<br/>manages pods| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>1.25+]
    Kueue -->|REQUIRED<br/>webhook TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>1.17+]

    %% Optional External Dependencies
    Kueue -.->|OPTIONAL<br/>metrics scraping| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Kueue -.->|OPTIONAL<br/>node provisioning| ClusterAutoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler]
    Kueue -.->|OPTIONAL<br/>TFJob, PyTorchJob, MPIJob| KubeflowOperator[Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>1.9+]
    Kueue -.->|OPTIONAL<br/>RayJob, RayCluster| RayOperator[Ray Operator<br/>1.3+]
    Kueue -.->|OPTIONAL<br/>JobSet resources| JobSet[JobSet<br/>0.8+]
    Kueue -.->|OPTIONAL<br/>AppWrapper resources| AppWrapper[AppWrapper<br/>1.1+]
    Kueue -.->|OPTIONAL<br/>multi-cluster dispatch| RemoteCluster["Remote Kubernetes Clusters<br/>(MultiKueue)"]

    %% Cloud Provider Integration (via Cluster Autoscaler)
    ClusterAutoscaler -.->|node scaling| CloudProvider["Cloud Provider API<br/>AWS/GCP/Azure"]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    %% (None - Kueue is standalone)

    %% Integration Points (components that USE Kueue)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|OPTIONAL<br/>UI for queue mgmt| Kueue
    DataSciencePipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|OPTIONAL<br/>auto job admission| Kueue
    Training[Training Operators] -.->|OPTIONAL<br/>managed by Kueue| Kueue

    %% CRDs Created/Managed by Kueue
    subgraph "CRDs Managed by Kueue"
        direction TB
        WorkloadCRD[Workload]
        ClusterQueueCRD[ClusterQueue]
        LocalQueueCRD[LocalQueue]
        ResourceFlavorCRD[ResourceFlavor]
        AdmissionCheckCRD[AdmissionCheck]
        ProvisioningConfigCRD[ProvisioningRequestConfig]
        MultiKueueConfigCRD[MultiKueueConfig]
        CohortCRD[Cohort]
        TopologyCRD[Topology]
    end

    Kueue -->|creates/manages| WorkloadCRD
